 295:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** *
 296:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** * \details 
 297:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** *   This API should be called first to be able to capture the active application 
 298:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** *   number that is actually the running application number.
