1330:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** *  the Bootloadable Application Verification Status field of the metadata section
1331:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** *  claims that the Bootloadable application is valid, the function returns
1332:Generated_Source\PSoC4/Bootloader.c **** *  CYRET_SUCCESS without further checksum calculation.
